data.text: I've been tryng to journal more lately. Apparently it's good to get your thoughts out on paper. I've been writing about the things I want to do when I turn nineteen (19) and it's been pretty interesting to see the things I come up with. It just seems like such a long time from now...
I really love reading. It's just so hard to find the time when I have so much school work. It really stressed me out! And today isn't any better.
But I am proud of myself, I read about seven (7) books last month and in the next month or so my goal is to read five (5) more.
